content:
Is there a reason why I can't see who is 8th by commits in the author list at

https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_stats.html

?
Oh it's Johannes Hoelzl I guess. How come his line stops?
I guess the lines end at his last commit.
But why is he not on the list of contributors?
Which list? I see him a few times on the stats page.
We did hide leanprover-community-bot's commits, so I wonder if that has something to do with what you're seeing.
Oh, I see. The numbers in the last column skip 8. Yes, that's probably leanprover-community-bot.
